    <h1>Glasgow Perl Mongers Social</h1>
    <h2>Thursday 2010-09-09</h2>

    <hr />

    <div>
        On Thursday 2010-09-09, the day after the second Wednesday of September,
        the <a href="http://glasgow.darkpan.com/">Glasgow Perl Mongers</a> will
        meet for the first time at <a href="http://www.thepotstill.co.uk/">The Pot Still</a>,
        for the first social gathering of the newly born group.
    </div>

